eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Breast cancer diagnostic at I and II stages;
* Adjuvant or neoadjuvant chemotherapy (≤50% of sessions completed);
* More than 18 years.

Exclusion Criteria:

* Current smoking
* Diabetic neuropathy;
* Hypertension uncontrolled;
* Heart failure;
* Clinical depression;
* Skeletal muscle impairment which not allow physical exercise.
